to make WordPress easy: themes that just do what you ask, plugins that don&#8217;t demand you be a developer. (You may notice we recommend [...]</p><p>The post <a href="http://getshopped.org/themes-and-design/wp-e-commerce-proud-to-partner-with-ithemes/">WP e-Commerce Proud to Partner with iThemes</a> appeared first on <a href="http://getshopped.org">GetShopped.org</a>.</p>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:10:"amandablum";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:2559:"<p>The team at <a title="WP e-Commerce Plugin Theme Partners" href="http://www.getshopped.org">WP e-Commerce</a> is proud to announce a new partnership with <a href="http://ithemes.com/">iThemes</a>. We love the team at iThemes personally, but the reason we really admire them is their ability to make WordPress easy: themes that just do what you ask, <a href="http://ithemes.com/find/plugins/">plugins</a> that don&#8217;t demand you be a developer. (You may notice we recommend <a href="http://ithemes.com/purchase/backupbuddy/">Backup Buddy</a> for your site backups whenever WPEC is upgraded).</p>\n<p>In particular, we love iThemes themes for WP e-Commerce. they&#8217;re easy to use and turn WP e-Commerce into a slick, clean, customizable shop in a flash. You&#8217;ll notice you can now purchase <a href="http://getshopped.org/premium-upgrades/premium-theme-2/">premium themes</a> in addition to plugins. We&#8217;re launching with two themes: <a href="http://getshopped.org/premium-upgrades/premium-theme-2/depot-theme-for-wp-e-commerce-by-ithemes/">Depot</a> and <a href="http://getshopped.org/premium-upgrades/premium-theme-2/market-theme-for-wp-e-commerce-by-ithemes/">Market</a>.<br />\n<a href="http://getshopped.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/depot-shopp-400x290.jpg"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-297678" title="depot-shopp-400x290" src="http://getshopped.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/depot-shopp-400x290.jpg" alt="" width="400" height="290" /></a><a href="http://getshopped.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/market-400x290.jpg"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-297675" title="market-400x290" src="http://getshopped.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/market-400x290.jpg" alt="" width="400" height="290" /></a></p>\n<div style="clear: both;"></div>\n<p>Both feature multiple page templates, a beautiful design that pushes products to the forefront. Depot is a clean theme with a focus on marketing, ideal for clothes or retail or anything you can dream up. Market is a sleek and smart theme that allows Grid View to really shine, while allowing customers to visualize products in a sensible way.</p>\n<p>The team at WP e-Commerce is working hard to bring new add ons to you, including a wealth of theming options in the new year. We&#8217;re thrilled to launch with a partner as experienced as iThemes.</p>\n<p>The post <a href="http://getshopped.org/themes-and-design/wp-e-commerce-proud-to-partner-with-ithemes/">WP e-Commerce Proud to Partner with iThemes</a> appeared first on <a href="http://getshopped.org">GetShopped.org</a>.</p>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:89:"http://getshopped.org/themes-and-design/wp-e-commerce-proud-to-partner-with-ithemes/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"1";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:56:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\