(642, 1, '2012-10-08 13:39:01', '2012-10-08 13:39:01', 'Zita Menyhart is a London based product designer. Shortly after graduating in 2009 from London Metropolitan University, she started her own design practice Zita Menyhart Studio, focusing on exclusive and distinctive contemporary furniture and lighting. Her aim is to create sentimental designs with a modern twist by applying emotional ergonomics.\r\n\r\n<h2>Awards</h2>\r\n2009: Runner up\r\n\r\n(Innovation Nation, Concept Products 2009)\r\n\r\n2009: Finalist-Soft Furnishings Category\r\n\r\n(The Young Designer Awards 2009)\r\n\r\n2008: First Prize for Best Design and Realisation\r\n\r\n(The Worshipful Company of Upholders)\r\n\r\n<h2>Exhibitions</h2>\r\n\r\n2011: Interiors UAE (Abu Dhabi, UAE)\r\n\r\n2010: Grand Designs Live (London, UK)\r\n\r\n2009: Ideal Home Show (London, UK)\r\n\r\n2009: Interiors Birmingham (Birmingham, UK)\r\n\r\n2008: Heard Gallery (London, UK)\r\n\r\n2008: New Designers Graduate Show (London, UK)\r\n\r\n2008: Frederick Parker Gallery (London, UK)<!--:--><!--:hu--><h3>Awards</h3>\r\n2009: Runner up\r\n\r\n(Innovation Nation, Concept Products 2009)\r\n\r\n2009: Finalist-Soft Furnishings Category\r\n\r\n(The Young Designer Awards 2009)\r\n\r\n2008: First Prize for Best Design and Realisation\r\n\r\n(The Worshipful Company of Upholders)<!--:-->', 'Bio', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2-revision-14', '', '', '2012-10-08 13:39:01', '2012-10-08 13:39:01', '', 2, 'http://zitamenyhart.com/news-section/2-revision-14/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
